{"tid":1248464,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"是日反思：有誠意啲，去人屋企拜訪？","createTime":"2019-06-21T12:53:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T12:55:19.000Z","uid":241639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2721484029a68bb9aea7a5b64c6754c30d9b8868","tid":1248464,"uid":241639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:53:44.000Z","msg":"見大家由朝企咗晚，但人哋都無反應，留喺度真係冇意思。<br />\n<br />\n衝，就輸一世；但一味睇人返工放工又無用。<br />\n<br />\n老母教落，做人最緊要係乜？誠意呀！<br />\n<br />\n直接登門拜訪會唔會有誠意啲？"},{"pid":"43d06bea27ad8b7e0c3262cce0772d72b4416fc4","tid":1248464,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">必睇!!!!!<br />\n認真, 咁多位義士<br />\n呢個係狗屋( 警察總部)<br />\n入面無野多, 狗最多, 軍火最多<br />\n再者軍火多, 你衝入去可以認為你想搶槍<br />\n實彈射擊你班友, 我唔想每年平反621<br />\n衝就一定, 但唔係狗屋<br />\n認清目標, 叫親你衝狗屋既, 一係三毛, 一係警犬, 一係有病<br />\n圍住, 守住狗屋就好足夠<br />\n唔好受任何網上/現場既人挑釁<br />\n你要守, 要挨<br />\n衝立會係唔比開會, 衝狗屋係無撚用, 佢地出唔到黎就得<br />\n有傳 狗已部署重兵4千, 前後夾擊, 一擊就夾死你地!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190621&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59743894\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190621%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59743894&d=84TmSRyL%2BgXW7nGZFnhDcgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=f522f211\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190621%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59743894&h=09f88b5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190621&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59743894</a></span></strong></span></blockquote>"}]}